## Change 4: Update Quick Reference

**If there's a "Quick Start" or "Common Patterns" section, add:**

```markdown
### Execute Python Code

```polyglot
// Initialize Python runtime
[w] |W.Runtime.Python3.11
(|) <requirements:pg.path << \\NoPath\\
(|) >env:pg.serial >> $py

// Execute Python code
[r] |RT.Python.Run.Code
(|) <env:pg.serial << $py
(|) <kwargs.value:pg.int << 42
(|) >result:pg.serial >> $result
(|) <code:pg.string << |U.String.Python""
[+] +"def compute(value:int)->dict:"
[+] -"   return dict(result=value * 2)"
```

**See:** [Runtime Wrappers](/docs/stdlib/wrappers/runtime-wrappers.md) for complete documentation
```

